sequenceDiagram
        autonumber
        actor User
        participant UI as Frontend
        participant MM as MetaMask
        participant NFT as InnovateDAONFT
        participant GOV as InnovateDAOGovernor
        participant T as Treasury

        rect rgb(250,250,250)
        Note over User,T: Phase 1 - Setup
        User->>UI: connect wallet
        UI->>MM: request account
        MM-->>UI: account
        UI->>MM: safeMint + delegate
        MM->>NFT: safeMint / delegate
        NFT-->>MM: ok
        end

        rect rgb(252,252,252)
        Note over User,T: Phase 2 - Create Proposal
        User->>UI: submit proposal
        UI->>MM: proposeWithDeposit
        MM->>GOV: proposeWithDeposit
        GOV->>T: receive deposit
        GOV-->>MM: proposalId
        end

        rect rgb(250,250,250)
        Note over User,T: Phase 3 - Vote
        User->>UI: cast vote
        UI->>MM: castVote
        MM->>GOV: castVote
        GOV->>NFT: getVotes(snapshot)
        NFT-->>GOV: voting power
        GOV-->>MM: vote recorded
        end

        Note over GOV: pass if quorum >= 60% and majority for
        User->>UI: execute succeeded proposal
        UI->>MM: execute
        MM->>GOV: execute
        GOV->>T: execute treasury action
        GOV-->>MM: success
